#: Schema for UI5 Tooling Configuration File (ui5.yaml)

?version.#: Framework version to use in this project

_name.#: Unique identifier for the project, for example: organization.product.project

_defs_0_resources-configuration-properti.#: By default, the UI5 Tooling expects *.properties files to be UTF-8 encoded.

_name.#: Unique identifier for the extension, for example: ui5-task-fearless-rock
